<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>Pedido Recebido - Café Belle Vie</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/site.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="header-container">
      <div class="logo"><h1><a href="/" style="color:white;text-decoration:none">Café Belle Vie</a></h1></div>
      <nav id="desktop-nav">
        <a href="/">Início</a>
        <a href="/produtos">Produtos</a>
        <a href="/cafeterias">Cafeterias</a>
        <a href="/admin" style="margin-left:12px;border-left:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);padding-left:12px;color:#fff;opacity:0.9;font-weight:600;">Admin</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main style="max-width:800px;margin:60px auto;text-align:center;padding:0 20px;">
    <h2>Pedido enviado com sucesso</h2>
    <p>Obrigado, <strong><%= nome %></strong>! Seu pedido (ID: <strong><%= id %></strong>) foi recebido.</p>
    <p>Total: <strong>R$ <%= total.toFixed(2) %></strong></p>
    <p style="margin-top:20px;"><a href="/" style="color:#8b6f47;text-decoration:none;">Voltar para a página inicial</a></p>
  </main>

  <footer style="background:#2c1810;color:white;text-align:center;padding:30px;margin-top:40px;">
    <p>&copy; Café Belle Vie</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
